  <summary date="2019-11-15T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Rebuilding Our Communities by Keeping aggregates Sustainable Act or the ROCKS Act 

This bill directs the Department of Transportation to establish a working group of federal, state, tribal, and local stakeholders to conduct a study on the regulatory and legislative improvements necessary to preserve access to covered resources and reduce the costs and environmental impacts of infrastructure projects. (Covered resources are materials used in the construction and maintenance of roads, buildings, and other facilities, including stone, sand, and gravel.)</summary>
